    "start": 478.93,
    "end": 481.49,
    "text": "one unit, so they sometimes understand",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 481.49,
    "end": 483.17,
    "text": "the meaning of a phrase, but not every",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 483.17,
    "end": 483.91,
    "text": "word in the phrase.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 484.217,
    "end": 486.257,
    "text": "This would mean that learning the phrase",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 486.257,
    "end": 489.017,
    "text": "can I have as a chunk to order",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 489.017,
    "end": 491.017,
    "text": "something at a coffee shop, for example,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 491.257,
    "end": 494.017,
    "text": "can I have a black coffee please would be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 494.017,
    "end": 496.937,
    "text": "easier than first learning how to use the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 496.937,
    "end": 499.457,
    "text": "modal verb can on its own.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 499.774,
    "end": 502.494,
    "text": "How can you apply chunking? What I",
