  },
  {
    "start": 519.926,
    "end": 522.606,
    "text": "is to read, but also to watch",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 522.606,
    "end": 525.566,
    "text": "series and films. Press pause,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 525.566,
    "end": 527.806,
    "text": "repeat what you've just heard, and go",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 527.806,
    "end": 530.406,
    "text": "again. Which brings us to our next tip,",
