    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 540.335,
    "end": 542.695,
    "text": "The aim is to imitate as close as",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 542.695,
    "end": 545.615,
    "text": "possible what you hear. It improves",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 545.615,
    "end": 547.935,
    "text": "your accent and trains your brain to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
